3. Use the AWS CLI against the Tigris endpoint to create the bucket, for example:
   ```bash
   aws s3 mb s3://harbor-awscli-${trial_id}
   ```
4. Upload the pre-existing file `/home/user/tigris-task/hello.txt` to the bucket:
